## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Character Info (XP & Level) ───
###

### Get character — includes xp, xpToNextLevel, unspentStatPoints
GET {{host}}/characters/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Stat Allocation ───
###

### Allocate a stat point to strength
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "strength"
}

### Allocate a stat point to constitution (recalculates max HP)
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "constitution"
}

### Allocate a stat point to intelligence (recalculates max mana)
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "intelligence"
}

### Allocate a stat point to dexterity
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "dexterity"
}

### Allocate a stat point to wisdom
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "wisdom"
}

### Allocate a stat point to charisma
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "charisma"
}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Invalid stat name — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "luck"
}

### No unspent points — should fail (400) if already spent all
POST {{host}}/characters/allocate-stat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stat": "strength"
}

###
## ─── XP Gain (via travel) ───
###

### Travel to a new town to earn XP (discovery + town visit + distance)
POST {{host}}/travel/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "destinationX": 74,
  "destinationY": 71
}

### Check travel status — will show XP gain when travel resolves
GET {{host}}/travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
